          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-terracotta to-terracotta-dark rounded-3xl p-8 text-white">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-5xl mb-4 block">🎯</span>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-2">¿Listo para prepararte?</h3>
